"      Actifed Compound Linctus (AE, BF, BH, BJ, CI, CY, EG, ET, GH, GM, GN, HK, IQ, IR, JO, KE, KW, LB, LR, LY, MA, ML, MR, MU, MW, NE, NG, OM, QA, SA, SC, SD, SL, SN, SY, TZ, UG, YE, ZA, ZM, ZW);",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      CoActifed (CA);",
